---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const schemas = [{
  "@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"TouristTrip",
  "name":"14-Day Tanzania Safari",
  "description":"Two-week comprehensive Tanzania safari covering all major parks at a relaxed pace.",
  "provider":{"@id":"https://gokilimanjarotreks.com/#organization"},
  "touristType":"Wildlife safari traveller",
  "url":"https://gokilimanjarotreks.com/safaris/14-day-tanzania-safari"
}];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="14-Day Tanzania Safari | Go Kilimanjaro Treks"
  description="Two-week comprehensive Tanzania safari covering all major parks at a relaxed pace."
  schemas={schemas}
>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="page-hero-eyebrow">Tanzania Safari Itinerary</span>
    <h1>14-Day Tanzania Safari.</h1>
    <p>Two-week comprehensive Tanzania safari covering all major parks at a relaxed pace.</p>
    <div class="hero-ctas">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Request a Quote &#x2192;</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/255677917500" class="btn-ghost" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#x1F4AC; WhatsApp Nelson</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-white">
  <div class="container" style="max-width:820px">
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Tanzania &amp; Zanzibar Explorer (14 Days / 13 Nights)</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Starting From USD 4,650 Per Person*</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Rates vary depending on season, accommodation category, and group size.</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Safari Overview</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">This 14-day luxury journey combines Tanzania's most iconic wildlife regions with the tropical beauty of Zanzibar. The experience moves from the wild savannahs of the Northern Circuit home to elephants, lions, and the Great Migration into the serene Indian Ocean coastline where white sand beaches and turquoise waters offer complete relaxation.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">It is a carefully balanced itinerary designed for adventure, romance, photography, and unforgettable lifetime memories.</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 1: Arrival in Tanzania - Welcome to Arusha</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Upon arrival at Kilimanjaro International Airport (JRO), you will be warmly welcomed by your safari representative and transferred to your lodge in Arusha, a peaceful town surrounded by green landscapes at the base of Mount Meru.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">This first evening is reserved for rest and recovery after your journey. You will settle in, relax, and prepare for the adventure ahead in a calm and comfortable environment.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Arusha Serena Hotel</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 2: Arusha National Park - Walking Safari &amp; Canoe Experience</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">After breakfast, begin your first wildlife experience with a guided walking safari inside Arusha National Park, accompanied by a professional ranger. This allows you to experience nature on foot, observing wildlife and landscapes from a close and authentic perspective.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Later, continue with a canoe experience on the lake, where you may see flamingos, hippos at a distance, and rich birdlife surrounding the water.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">In the afternoon, return to your lodge for relaxation and safari preparation briefing for the journey ahead.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Arusha Serena Hotel</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Full Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 3: Tarangire National Park - Land of Elephants</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Depart for Tarangire National Park, a scenic wilderness known for its massive elephant herds and ancient baobab trees rising above golden plains.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a full-day game drive through diverse habitats where lions, giraffes, zebras, buffaloes, wildebeest, and many bird species roam freely. The Tarangire River attracts large concentrations of wildlife, making every moment of exploration rewarding.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Maramboi Tented Lodge</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Full Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 4: Ngorongoro Highlands - Crater Edge Experience</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Journey through the scenic Rift Valley and arrive at the Ngorongoro Highlands. Along the way, you may stop briefly at local craft markets for cultural interaction and souvenir opportunities.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Later, continue toward the Ngorongoro Conservation Area where cool mountain air and dramatic landscapes set the tone for the next day's crater exploration.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Ngorongoro Serena Safari Lodge</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Full Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 5: Ngorongoro Crater - Africa's Natural Sanctuary</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Descend into the Ngorongoro Crater, one of the most remarkable wildlife destinations on Earth. This natural amphitheatre hosts an incredible density of animals including lions, elephants, buffaloes, hippos, hyenas, and the rare black rhino.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a picnic lunch inside the crater while surrounded by breathtaking scenery and abundant wildlife before ascending back to the rim in the afternoon.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Serengeti Serena Safari Lodge</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Full Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 6: Serengeti Central - Into the Endless Plains</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Travel into Serengeti National Park, where vast golden plains stretch endlessly into the horizon. Begin your first game drive in Central Serengeti, an area rich in predators and year-round wildlife activity.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Expect encounters with lions, leopards, cheetahs, elephants, and large herds of grazing animals across open savannah landscapes.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Serengeti Serena Safari Lodge</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Full Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 7: Serengeti to Northern Corridor - Migration Journey Begins</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">After breakfast, enjoy a scenic game drive as you move deeper into the Serengeti ecosystem toward the northern region. The landscape changes gradually into more remote and untouched wilderness.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">This area is famous for seasonal wildlife movement, especially the Great Migration, offering opportunities to witness vast herds crossing open plains.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Migration Tented Camp (Northern Serengeti)</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Full Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 8: Northern Serengeti - Mara River Wilderness</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Spend a full day exploring the Northern Serengeti and the iconic Mara River region. This is one of Africa's most dramatic wildlife stages, where large herds gather near the riverbanks and predators remain close by.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">You will witness the intense river crossings where survival instincts take center stage in a powerful display of nature.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Migration Tented Camp</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Full Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 9: Fly to Zanzibar - Arrival in Paradise</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">After breakfast, transfer to the airstrip for your flight to Zanzibar Island. Upon arrival, you will be welcomed and transferred to your beach resort along the Indian Ocean.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">The rest of the day is dedicated to relaxation-white sand beaches, warm ocean breeze, and peaceful surroundings mark the beginning of your island escape.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Zuri Zanzibar Hotel</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 10: Prison Island &amp; Nakupenda Sandbank</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a full-day ocean excursion exploring Prison Island and the beautiful Nakupenda Sandbank. Discover historical sites, interact with giant tortoises, and later relax on a pristine sandbank surrounded by crystal-clear waters.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">A fresh seafood lunch is served on the beach as you enjoy swimming, snorkeling, and sunbathing in a tropical paradise setting.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Zuri Zanzibar Hotel</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 11: Kizimkazi Dolphin Experience &amp; Stone Town Tour</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Head south for a marine experience in Kizimkazi, where you may observe dolphins in their natural ocean habitat. After beach relaxation and lunch, continue to Stone Town for a guided cultural tour.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Explore narrow streets, historic architecture, spice markets, and centuries of cultural fusion shaped by African, Arab, and European influences.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Return to your resort in the evening.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Zuri Zanzibar Hotel</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 12: Sea Turtles &amp; Spice Experience</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">After breakfast, visit a sea turtle sanctuary where you can observe and interact with turtles in clear lagoon waters.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Later, choose between a spice farm experience or a visit to Jozani Forest to see the rare red colobus monkeys in their natural environment.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Return to your resort for a relaxing evening by the ocean.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Zuri Zanzibar Hotel</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 13: Zanzibar Leisure - Final Island Moments</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Enjoy a slow and relaxing day at the beach. This is your time to unwind, walk along the shoreline, enjoy spa treatments, or explore local markets for souvenirs.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">The day is designed for complete relaxation before departure.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Accommodation: Zuri Zanzibar Hotel</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--amber-cta);margin:32px 0 12px">Day 14: Departure - Farewell Tanzania</h2>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">After breakfast, enjoy your final moments in Zanzibar before transfer to the airport for your international flight.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">As your journey comes to an end, you leave with unforgettable memories of wildlife adventures, cultural discoveries, and the serene beauty of Tanzania and Zanzibar.</p>
    <p style="font-size:1rem;color:var(--text);line-height:1.78;margin-bottom:14px">Board Basis: Half Board</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Ready to <em>Plan This Safari</em>?</h2>
    <p>Talk to Nelson about your dates, group size, and what you most want to see. He responds personally within 24 hours.</p>
    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="font-size:1.05rem;padding:18px 40px">Request a Quote &#x2192;</a>
      <a href="https://wa.me/255677917500" class="btn-wa" style="font-size:1rem" target="_blank" rel="noopener">&#x1F4AC; WhatsApp Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</BaseLayout>
